                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>I play at Riches - to appease</l>
                    <l>The Clamoring for Gold - </l>
                    <l>It kept me from a Thief,<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 I think, </l>
                    <l>For often, overbold </l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>With Want, and Opportunity -</l>
                    <l>I<add type="alternate" extent="could">might</add>
 could have done a Sin </l>
                    <l>And been Myself that<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
<add type="alternate" extent="easy">distant</add>
 easy Thing </l>
                    <l>An <app type="emendation"><lem>independant</lem><rdg>independent</rdg></app>
 Man - </l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>But often as my lot<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 displays </l>
                    <l>Too hungry to be borne</l>
                    <l>I deem Myself what I<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 would be - </l>
                    <l>And<add type="alternate" extent="novel Comforting">so much comforting</add>
 novel Comforting </l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>My Poverty and I derive - </l>
                    <l>We question if the Man -<app type="division"><lem><pb/></lem></app>
 </l>
                    <l>Who own - Esteem the<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 Opulence -</l>
                    <l>As we - Who never Can - </l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Should ever these exploring<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 Hands </l>
                    <l>Chance Sovreign on a<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 Mine - </l>
                    <l>Or in the long - uneven<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 term </l>
                    <l>To win, become<add type="alternate" extent="their">my</add>
 their<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 turn -</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l><add type="alternate" extent="How">&#x27;Tis</add>
How fitter they will be -<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
<add type="alternate" extent="for">by</add>
 for Want - </l>
                    <l>Enlightening so well - </l>
                    <l>I know not which,<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 Desire, or<add type="alternate" extent="Grant -">Right - &amp;#x2022; sight</add>
 Grant - </l>
                    <l>Be<add type="alternate" extent="wholly">chiefest &amp;#x2022; utmost</add>
 wholly beautiful - </l>
                </lg>

